description: The file defines a React component named SearchPage that provides an advanced search interface for searching through documents, with filter options such as vendor, category, total amounts, and date ranges. It handles user inputs, performs API calls to fetch search results, and displays the results via a DocumentList component.

methods.name: submit
methods.description: An asynchronous function triggered to perform the search operation by calling the API with current filter parameters, managing loading and error states, and updating search results.
